    An implementation of the model object ‘ETyped Element Configuration’.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Visible
    • Editable
    • Disabled
    • Location
    • Category
    • Control
    • Control Configuration
    • Input Type
    • Form Input Group
    • Placeholder
